  <prompt>
    Author integration test for the upload pipeline (066 orchestrator + 067/068/069 enrichment + 072 persistence + 071 shape). Test simulates uploading a 50-page synthetic PDF text content through `ChatDocumentEndpoints.UploadDocumentAsync` and asserts:
    - All 4 enriched fields populated (`SummaryText`, `ClassifiedDocType`, `Sections`, `PageCount`)
    - Total enrichment latency ≤4s per architecture §6.1
    - Cosmos write completed (read-back assertion via Redis or Cosmos)
    - No tier-1-banned content in logs (textContent, summary text, classification text)
  </prompt>

  <role>SPAARKE platform QA / test engineer. Expert in WebApplicationFactory integration tests + performance assertions.</role>

  <goal>
    `UploadPipelineIntegrationTests.cs` exists in `tests/integration/Sprk.Bff.Api.IntegrationTests/UploadPipeline/`. Test runs end-to-end with mocked Azure OpenAI (fast deterministic responses) + in-memory Redis + Cosmos emulator (or test double). Asserts ≤4s total + enriched field population + tier-1 log safety.
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      Per architecture §6.1 — total latency target for 50-page PDF enrichment: ~2-4s. The 4 parallel paths (classify ~250ms, summarize ~250ms, manifest extract ~50ms, RAG index ~1500-3500ms — the dominant tail) complete via `Task.WhenAll`. This test makes the latency budget binding.
    </background>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>tests/integration/Sprk.Bff.Api.IntegrationTests/</file>
      <file>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Api/Ai/ChatDocumentEndpoints.cs</file>
    </relevant-files>
  </context>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-015">Log assertion: NO log line in the captured stream contains textContent OR summary text OR classification label text body.</constraint>
    <constraint source="architecture §6.1">Latency target: total ≤4s for 50-page synthetic text input.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">Mock `IOpenAiClient` for deterministic latency (avoid real LLM cost in CI); use in-memory Redis + Cosmos emulator OR test doubles.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">Test the parallel-execution path — assert `Task.WhenAll` semantics by confirming total ≤ sum of slowest individual call + overhead.</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>projects/spaarke-ai-platform-chat-routing-redesign-r1/architecture/stateful-chat-architecture.md</file>
      <file>projects/spaarke-ai-platform-chat-routing-redesign-r1/spec.md</file>
      <file>projects/spaarke-ai-platform-chat-routing-redesign-r1/CLAUDE.md</file>
